T09:34:21.000Z","msg":"建議你買個膠盒（生魚仔嗰隻）困住條鬥魚放係缸入面養（無自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />） <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 燈魚就隨便啦"},{"pid":"2485243811b5c1bcd7dad963a846e26934afb23d","tid":1598031,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:35:39.000Z","msg":"我養過鬥魚 + 燈魚 + 彩雀 , 又無事喎, 啲彩雀仲可以生 bb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7ba46e86aa81c1129c2ff97c3e51f21e4fead0","tid":1598031,"uid":103990,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:38:00.000Z","msg":"圖入面既草都易養，水温最好keep 26-29度內，中性水就okay , 燈方面用圖入面個隻我就已經轉左做偏向白黃色，姐係似自然光，幾個星期d草已經生出水面。<br />\n<br />\n濾水器個濾箱要大d,  可以放多d濾材，咁先養到夠菌，菌要點養就google下，唔難。<br />\n<br />\n利申：幾個月前先開始養魚，暫時差唔多個半月冇死過魚。<br />\n<br />\n希望幫到你<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/05x9ZFg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F05x9ZFg.jpg&h=4ccfe96d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4837c7736b95a19a286a06ce191289b8b96a4a6e","tid":1598031,"uid":280385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2485243811b5c1bcd7dad963a846e26934afb23d","tid":1598031,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:35:39.000Z","msg":"我養過鬥魚 + 燈魚 + 彩雀 , 又無事喎, 啲彩雀仲可以生 bb <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T09:40:55.000Z","msg":"我試過 龍魚 火箭 波子 燈魚 泰國虎  英鵡一缸 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb792b76b157d180012e5a9b72355dae14026c73","tid":1598031,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4837c7736b95a19a286a06ce191289b8b96a4a6e","tid":1598031,"uid":280385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":